GCP_HT.describes: As per DGPS value in meter

W_POP.describes: Population of Ward as per 2011 census data

W_ID.describes: It will start with W followed by 001 for ward 1, 002 for ward 2 and so on

W_PROP.describes: Total number of properties based on property survey; will be updated after survey

GCP_LAT.describes: Geographical coordinates (Latitude) as per DGPS for the location in decimal degree like  25°19'40.52"N

W_AREA.describes: Ward area for each ward in sq. km as per GIS- based calculation

GCP_LON.describes: Geographical coordinates (longitude) as per DGPS for the location in Degree Minutes  Seconds like 83° 0'31.03"E

SURROUND.describes: Brief description about surroundings in all the directions East, West, North and South

CLASS.describes: Class Code and Sub Class Code will be

SUB_CLASS.describes: updated as per AMRUT guidelines given in Annexure XI, Volume II of the Inception  Report

GCP_PHID.describes: Unique ID for Photo will start with GCP ID followed by 4 digits of Year (like 2018) then  month (like for June it will be 06) then date  (01) and then 2 digits in incremental order  (like 01 to 99)

W_HH.describes: Total number of households as per census data

W_HH_SC.describes: Total number of household having Sewer connection  based  on  consumer  database  survey; will be updated after survey

W_HH_WC.describes: Total number of household having water connection based on consumer survey; will be  updated after survey

TIME_ST.describes: Date of DGPS survey (DD-Month-YYYY) like 30 June 2018

W_SL_AR.describes: Total area of slum based on slum survey for GIS base map preparation (in Ha)
